    "offer_browser_tts": "true",
    "panels": [
      {
        "text": "**Scenario 1: Should Smart Sensors in Classrooms Monitor Student Engagement?**\n\nSome schools are considering using AI-driven smart cameras and motion sensors to track student attention and engagement in class. The system analyzes facial expressions, eye movement, and body posture to determine if students are focused.",
        "imageUrl": "https://images.code.org/6ac486aa087c71b1f2304d688bd78c29-installing-new-surveillance-equipment-2025-02-11-12-50-32-utc.jpg",
        "key": "undefined-ae4d7072-fc5f-4cfa-9fb4-dd5c9540d2ea",
        "layout": "text-top-left"
      },
      {
        "text": "**Roles**\n- High School Student\n-  High School Teacher\n- School Administrator\n- Tech Company Representative\n",
        "imageUrl": "https://images.code.org/7b093a027b5be78539d4069d92973e32-people-employees-icons-on-wooden-blocks-business-2024-10-11-02-59-12-utc.jpg",
        "key": "undefined-96e1ca3b-ed52-4eaa-b731-18f40f537e1a",
        "layout": "text-top-right"
      },
      {
        "text": "**Discussion Questions:**\n- Can AI accurately measure student engagement, or could it unfairly label certain students? \n- How might constant monitoring of student engagement affect mental health and classroom participation? \n- Who should have access to student engagement data, and how might it be misused?",
        "imageUrl": "https://images.code.org/d2118d1712dcaac218f15147f55a40f0-painted-light-bulb-with-word-idea-and-colored-blan-2023-11-27-05-17-12-utc.jpg",
        "key": "undefined-3b8137d9-fcb7-43b7-8302-60cb3bf5ae98",
        "layout": "text-top-right"
      },
      {
        "text": "**Propose a Decision**\n- Work with your group to create a proposal that addresses the scenario. \n- Your goal is to find a solution that feels fair to all roles.\n- Be ready to explain how your proposal considers each perspective.\n",
        "imageUrl": "https://images.code.org/916cf5d643122f2099f30b6bec11aa74-balance-scale-placed-on-top-of-a-green-paper-cutou-2024-10-28-22-26-31-utc.jpg",
        "key": "computer-systems-lesson12-scenario-1-5babb39a-56a8-4610-bf06-154f025b2367"
      }
    ]
  },
